(565, '5a0d59c2e914587ec1459665', 'GO', 'Cour de Honau - La Wantzenau (67)', 'Cour de Honau - La Wantzenau', 'LA WANTZENAU (67) A few minutes from Strasbourg, in a 5-hectare park on the edge of the Robertsau forest, the Honau Court, sports and relaxation club offers you state-of-the-art equipment, and exceptional. The Cour de Honau is one of the most beautiful venues in Europe that welcomes you 7 days a week for specific or localized muscle-building, cardio training with a constantly evolving equipment park, your training sessions under the guidance of state-qualified instructors who, from the first session, take stock of the situation in order to establish a specialized program. More than 100 group lessons per week, all levels, from choreography to postural, aquagym, physical and especially pleasure. - 8 tennis courts, - Swimming pool with jets of massage - Jacuzzi - Spa - Saunas and hammams, - Pressure shower and terrace - Solarium of 150 m² with deckchairs, umbrellas for moments of pure relaxation ... For your children of 3 months guard free and supervised on more than 150 m ² and also outdoors. The business tickets allow to come at any time and to benefit from all the sports services Not nominative, they give you access to all the services of the club, without restriction, during 4 hours. Ticket valid for 9 months. Child offer: 1 business ticket purchased = 2 tickets Children under 12 offered (on site) - 2 free hours of childcare from 3 months to 12 years. Good to know: Open 7 days a week, Opening hours Monday to Thursday from 9 am to 11 pm, Friday, Saturday, Sunday and public holidays from 9 am to 9 pm.', 'LA WANTZENAU (67)\r\n\r\nA quelques minutes de Strasbourg, dans un parc de 5 hectares, en lisière de la forêt de la Robertsau, la Cour de Honau, club de sport et de détente vous offre un équipement de pointe, une ambiance conviviale et exceptionnelle.\r\n\r\nLa Cour de Honau, c\'est d\'abord l\'une des plus belles salles d\'Europe qui vous accueille 7 jours s