(1227, '5a0d5a2be914587ec14597e1', 'GO', 'Escape Game - Coffret Cadeau Escape Hunt Coffret C', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description Gift box price valid for the whole team: 99 € / 5 ≈ 20 € per person only! Puzzle mystery to reconstruct in order to decipher the reservation code: 1 x session valid on one of the national centers (7 days a week, holidays and holidays included). PARIS - BORDEAUX - AIX-MARSEILLE - NANCY - CLERMONT-FERRAND - LA ROCHELLENANTES - METZ - BRUSSELS - TOULOUSE (coming soon) - BELFORT (soon) ESCAPE HUNT, THE ADVENTURE IN 60MINUTES CHRONO | 1 TEAM - 1 INVESTIGATION - 1 HOUR - LOCAL ENJOYS AND GREAT PLACES - A LUDAKY ADVENTURE FULL OF SURPRISES AND REBUILDINGS - A BEVERAGE &amp; PHOTO OFFERED AFTER THE ACTIVITY - MULTIPLE ROOMS AVAILABLE ON THE SAME THEME TO CHALLENGE More info: information: Click here En route for an unusual and exceptional adventure where your child&#39;s soul seems to escape time ... The game begins as soon as this box is opened with a first enigma to solve ... For young and old, this new entertainment life size makes it possible to slip into the skin of an investigator and to live an authentic adventure made of twists and turns. In teams of 2 to 5, players must use all their research, observation and logic capabilities. At the heart of an astonishing setting, the slightest clue is essential to solve one of the many puzzles and manage to escape from one of the rooms in less than 60 minutes. An investigation into the famous Jack the Ripper, a murder in Cézanne&#39;s studio or a crazy pursuit in the metropolitan, the budding detectives will surely break through all these mysteries. More information: Click Here', '\n     Description détaillée \n                		Tarif coffret cadeau valable pour l\'équipe entière : 99€ / 5 ≈ 20€ par personne seulement !\nPuzzle mystère à reconstituer afin de déchiffrer le code de réservation : 1 x session valable sur l\'un des centres nationaux (7j/7, vacances et jours fériés inclus).&nbsp;&