(82, '5a0d5978e914587ec14594f6', 'GO', 'Gaumont Valenciennes (59)', 'Gaumont Valenciennes', 'Valencian (59). \r\n\r\n15 rooms. 3700 places. Parking 800 spaces. Accessibility for people with reduced mobility. \r\n\r\nThe «CHEQUE CINEMA LOCAL VALENCIENNE LIEVIN» is valid for all films in 2D or 3D *, in the GAUMONT VALENCIENNES or PATHE LIEVIN cinemas. This ticket can also be used at no extra charge for the Bolshoi Ballet retransmissions or for the retransmission of the performances of La Comédie Française. Convenient ! Download the free Androide application from the Gaumont and Pathé cinemas: always available for IPHONE on APP STORE and on the mobile internet on cinegaumontpathe.mobi. With your CINEMA CHECK, take advantage of the e-ticket to go directly to your session and accumulate your loyalty points without presenting your cinema card! * Based on a standard 3D session included (any supplement such as 3D glasses and additional service will be paid extra) and out of special session.\r\n\r\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n\r\nTickets are delivered about 9 to 10 days after your order\r\n\r\n1. For the delivery mode of your order on the website, you can choose the Predict service. All you have to do is to enter your mobile phone number in the field provided.\r\n\r\n2. Once your order is done, we will send a text message proposing with a list of dates and time’s slots for delivery.\r\n\r\n3. You answer “1” or “2” by text message according to your availability (price of a standard text message) or you go to www.dpd.fr/destinataires for more choices (for another dates, address or delivery in relays, to a neighbor or in DPD agency).\r\n\r\n4. On the scheduled delivery day, you will receive a text message reminding you of the delivery time slot chosen!\r\n\r\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~', 'Valencienne (59)\r\n\r\n. 15 salles\r\n. 3700 places\r\n. Parking 800 places\r\n. Accessibilité aux personnes à mobilité réduite.\r\n\r\nLe « CHEQUE CINEMA LOCAL VALENCIENNE 