(315, '5a0d5c93e914587ec145980c', 'GO', 'Azium Escalade - Lyon (69)', 'Azium Escalade - Lyon', 'Confluence Trade and Leisure Center The Azcal Escalade Universe - Relaxation &amp; indoor leisure! The free time has changed. Times, rhythms, cravings, habits ... everything accelerates and leads us to reinvent the relaxation in the pure state! A true parenthesis in the heart of the urban landscape, Azium is the ideal place to live interior sensations ... indoors. Dive with open arms into the universe of Azium and breathe! Your idea of ​​leisure will never again be the same ... Experience will become ritual, pleasure and emotion will become escape. Accessible without interruption and without limit, from morning to night, Azium opens up to your desires. A true bubble of freedom, coming to breathe the time of a break, a meal or a day. Do it for you! A temperate atmosphere in all seasons, a continuous air and a pleasant light will make you change your opinion on indoor climbing! In an area with clean volumes, lighted by large bay windows, climbing Azium version stands out thanks to these 800 m² of walls staggered between 6 and 22 meters. With nearly 250 routes, from levels 4 to 8, seasoned and beginner climbers will find booties at their feet. Alongside the classic lines, discover 10 lines equipped with a self-assured system to climb alone in total autonomy and in total safety. A comfortable climbing area, an incredible view on the building and La Confluence ... it&#39;s climbing Azium!', 'Pôle de Commerce et de Loisirs de Confluence\r\n\r\nL’Univers Escalade Azium – \r\n\r\nDétente &amp; loisir intérieur !\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLe temps libre a changé. Durées, rythmes, envies, habitudes… tout s’accélère et nous amène à réinventer la détente à l’état pur ! \r\nVéritable parenthèse au cœur du paysage urbain, Azium est le lieu idéal pour vivre des sensations intérieures… en intérieur.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPlongez à bras ouverts dans l’univers d’Azium et respirez ! \r\nVotre idée du