(353, '5a0d59a0e914587ec14595d3', 'GO', 'DéfiPlanet -\r\n Dienné (86)(e\'billet)', 'DéfiPlanet -\r\n Dienné', 'Dienné - (86) - DéfiPlanet Nature and Fun Park Less than 30 minutes from Poitiers-Futuroscope In a 50 hectare nature park, DéfiPlanet &#39;le Parc will plunge you into a magical adventure where you will experience a Naturally Different Experience. All the actors of your visit, you will have to make the right choices and correctly answer the puzzles to hope to save the Planet from a Serious Danger! But do not worry: &quot;No need to be a super hero to save the Planet.&quot; Throughout your journey you will be helped by your guide &quot;Petit Sabot&quot;. Thanks to him, you will first make acquaintance with different villages and animals of the world (Dromadaires, Baudets du Poitou, Lamas etc ...). You will then enter a magical forest where sprites and goblins will also help you in your quest for truth. You will still have to be attentive to the little beings of the forest, avoid their jokes or climb on the roof of the forest to reach the final test and hope to reach your ultimate goal: to save the Blue Planet. Allow about 3H30 to 4H of visit / Possible picnic on the park and snack in season / Free for the under 5 years. Défiplanet &#39;is also a residential park with unusual accommodation: tree huts, houses and castle in the branches, yurts, chalets, houses snail, houses mushroom, hen, rabbit and houses of Farfadets, Gites de France, caravans, square of stars). On the spot, different modes of catering: Défi&#39;Gourmet, Plancha and Chaudron des farfadets, Snack, Boutique ... And many sporting activities of nature accessible to the map or package: Adventure trail, Horse riding, Archery, treasures, Mini golf, Disc golf, Mountain biking, Wellness area ...', 'Dienné - (86) - \r\n\r\nDéfiPlanet le Parc Nature et Ludique \r\n\r\nA moins de 30 minutes de Poitiers-Futuroscope\r\n\r\nDans un Domaine nature de 50Ha, DéfiPlanet’ le Parc vous&nbsp; plongera dans une ave