(460, '5a0d59b1e914587ec1459623', 'GO', 'Koezio (Carré Sénart) - Lieusaint (77)', 'Koezio (Carré Sénart) - Lieusaint', 'Lieusaint (77) The great adventure game you are the heroes! The Concept DISCOVER A NEW WAY TO LIVE YOUR RECREATION NEAR PARIS: THE KOEZIO MISSION Koezio is a great adventure game in team, to live with family, friends or colleagues, which will make you live all the emotions. In a park of 6000 m² indoor 100% thematized, you will have to cross 5 Worlds, to pass collective tests of action and reflection, to find clues to solve the Final Enigma ... Koezio mixes intelligently real and virtual, physical implication and knowledge by helping to develop essential human values: Team spirit, self-help, self-esteem and trust. Koezio proposes to you to live almost 2h of pleasure for the head and the legs in total disconnection! After the Mission: a bar and a quality catering area welcome you in an atmosphere disconnected from everyday life. The Mission KOEZIO: AN INNOVATIVE LEISURE DESTINATION FOR ALL! This adventure game is accessible from 1m40 and without age requirement. Everyone can have fun in this interactive role-playing game: men, women, children, teenagers and adults. Whatever your physical level you can bring to your team and develop your strategies in a fun and exciting way! Total number of participants: 2 to 5 per team, Additional info: a Mission Classic &#39;= 5 worlds to cross, 4 clues to pick up, 1 final puzzle to solve. Reservations required School days: Tuesday: 19h-22h Wednesday: 14h-22h Thursday: 19h-22h Friday: 18h-23h Saturday: 11h-23h Sunday: 11h-18h School holidays: Monday: 1pm to 7pm Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday: -22h Friday: 13h-23h Saturday: 11h-23h Sunday: 11h-18h - Open all year round -', 'Lieusaint (77)\r\n\r\nLe grand jeu d\'aventure dont vous êtes les héros !\r\n\r\n\r\nLe Concept\r\n&nbsp;\r\nDÉCOUVREZ UNE NOUVELLE FAÇON DE VIVRE VOS LOISIRS PRÈS DE PARIS : LA MISSION KOEZIO\r\n\r\nKoezio est un grand jeu d’Aventure en équipe, à v