(534, '5a0d59bde914587ec1459650', 'GO', 'Aquarium de Paris - Cinéaqua (75)', 'Aquarium de Paris - Cinéaqua', 'Paris (16)\r\n\r\nMuch more than an aquarium! Discover more than 10,000 fish, 32 great sharks and interactive activities for the whole family. In the gardens of Trocadero, in the heart of Paris, share a moment of escape and relaxation. The Aquarium of Paris takes you in a dream mode to better understand the marine world. Understanding &amp; Dreaming in Family! ... This new exhibition highlights the know-how of the Aquarium of Paris, combining discovery and entertainment. Young and old alike will enjoy sharing a 360 ° immersion in the marine world with a rich and varied program of activities. Photo exhibits, creative workshops, creative workshops, video projections and much more will take visitors to a dream world. Enjoy the entertainment program and show all day. Enjoy the nourishment of one of our emblematic species: shark, moray, octopus ..... Extend the adventure by a lunch in our restaurant and its view on the Réunion-Mayotte basin. Access: Metro Station Iéna (line 9) - Metro Station Trocadéro (line 6 or 9), RER C Champs de Mars .. Open all year: From 10h to 19h (closing of the boxes at 18h). Annual closure on 14 July. The Aquarium de Paris now opens its doors at night on the first Saturday of the month. Enjoy our formula &quot;Free visit + 1 glass of champagne&quot;.', 'Paris (16)\r\n\r\nBien plus qu\'un aquarium !\r\nDécouvrez plus de 10 000 poissons, 32 grands requins et des activités interactives pour toute la famille.\r\n\r\nDans les jardins du Trocadéro, en plein coeur de Paris, partagez un moment d\'évasion et de détente. \r\n\r\nL\'Aquarium de Paris vous plonge dans un mode de rêve pour mieux comprendre l\'univers marin.\r\n\r\nComprendre &amp; Rêver en Famille !\r\nINSERT INTO `eyca_quality` (`discount_id`, `eyca_id`, `CATEGORIES`, `NAME`, `VENDOR`, `DESCRIPTION_ENG`, `DESCRIPTION_LOCAL`, `EMAIL`, `PHONE`, `WEB`, `STREET`, `CITY`, `ZIP`, `COUNTRY`, `REGION`, `GEO`, `TAGS`, `IMAGE`, `PRIX`, `last_touch`) VALUES
(567, '5a0d5c9be914587ec145985c', 'GO', 'Piscine de Mourenx (64)', 'Piscine de Mourenx', 'Mourenx (64) AQUATIC AREA Sports pool: At a constant temperature, this 25m pool with 6 water lines is ideally suited to swimming and aquatic activities. Balneo-ludic pool: This pool, with massaging benches , water games and geysers, will respond perfectly to your desires of relaxation. Wading pool: Spend a moment of sweetness and complicity with your little ones by making them discover the joys of the aquatic environment. Slide: This giant slide will take you on incredible descents. For crazy laughter between young and old, it&#39;s ideal! Solarium: Come enjoy the first rays of sunshine, well set in sunbeds of the solarium equipped with misters or comfortably lying on the wide grassed beach in the shade of the palm trees. Give yourself a moment of total relaxation ... THE ESPACE DETENTE is at your disposal to offer you the best of well-being: Sauna, Hammam, massaging jets, relaxation area and solarium terrace. Ideal after your water activities session.', 'Mourenx (64)\r\n\r\nL’ESPACE AQUATIQUE\r\n\r\nBassin sportif : \r\n&nbsp;A température constante, ce bassin de 25m avec 6 lignes d\'eau est idéalement adapté aux pratiques de la natation et des activités aquatiques\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nBassin balnéo-ludique :\r\nCe bassin, avec banquettes massantes, jeux d\'eau et geysers, répondra parfaitement a vos envies de détente. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nPataugeoire :\r\nPassez un moment de douceur et de complicité avec vos tout petits en leur faisant découvrir les joies du milieu aquatique.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nToboggan :\r\nCe toboggan géant vous entraînera dans des descentes incroyables. Pour des fous rires entre petits et grands, c\'est idéal !\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nSolarium :\r\nVenez profiter des premiers rayons de soleil, bien installé dans les transats du solarium équipé de brumisateurs ou confortablement allongé sur la grande plage engazonnée à l\'ombre des palmiers.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAcco