(686, '5a0d5ca0e914587ec1459888', 'GO', 'Mini Châteaux et Aquarium de Touraine (37)', 'Mini Châteaux et Aquarium de Touraine', ' LUSSAULT SUR LOIRE (3 minutes from Amboise - 37) MINI CHATEAUX VAL DE LOIRE, another look at the biggest castles of the Loire in miniature. AQUARIUM OF THE VALLEY OF LOIRE, the great show of the Loire. Mini Châteaux Loire Valley: In a green theater, in the heart of a landscaped park of 2 hectares, nestle no less than 45 miniatures of the most beautiful castles of the Loire Valley ... Mini-châteaux, it is the opportunity to discover , or rediscover the most prestigious castles of the Loire by giant steps. Faithful reproductions on a scale of 1 / 30th integrated in an environment of extraordinary nature, 2000 bonsaïs, 10 000 figurines, as many details to marvel. The plant labyrinth: a Renaissance classic for delighted children! The Roseraie de Ronsard: an enchantment of colors and scents. The small trains: 6 miniature railway networks cross the two hectares of the park for a dreamlike trip ... and jerky! Opening hours: From 1 April to 31 May: 10.30 am to 7 pm From 1 June to 31 July: 10 am to 7 pm From 1 to 23 August: 10 am to 8 pm From 24 to 31 August: 10 am to 7 pm From 1 September to 15 November : from 10:30 am to 6:00 pm Closure of the boxes 1 hour before. Reopening: Spring 2010. Aquarium of the Loire Valley 2 million liters of water and more than 40 basins to discover the giants that inhabit the Loire, but also all the emblematic species of the rivers and oceans of the whole world. An exceptional scenic route offered to the whole family to discover, have fun, dream. The Loire from its source to the estuary reveals its diversity: from the minnow of a few grams to the sturgeons of more than 2 meters, all the casting of the great wild river is gathered. The Naturalist&#39;s Cabin, a playground for touching, exploring and feeling. The oceans reveal the Cabinet of Curiosities with its corals and seahorses or the Moon-fish and other Barracuda 