(1139, '5a0d5a1ce914587ec14597be', 'GO', 'Azur Park GassinBaby Pass (2-6 ans) - 15 attractio', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description Rides, treats and sensations ... As every year, the Azur Park settles near the roundabout of Foux in Gassin! More than 35 attractions for young and old await you. The Extreme Pass includes 1 tour for the following 5 attractions: Sky Rider, Ejection Seat, Typhoon Flight Men, Playball, Atmosfear. The Fun Pass includes 1 tour for 19 attractions including: Typhoon (chair), Bumper Boat, Dschunke, Big Wheel, Playball, River Slide, Hot Air Balloon, Fun House, Slide, Accrobranche, Carrousel 1900, Cinema 7D, Trampoline, Atmosfear, Stargate, Crazy Mouse. The Baby Pass includes 1 tour for 15 attractions including: Mini Pouss-Pouss, Formula 1, Tacots 1900, Train des Pignes, Bounty, Toboggan, Aladin, Petit Manège, Super Rally or La Pomme, Cuzco, Jumping Frog, Dragoon, Caroussel 1900 , Trampoline. The Little Pass includes 1 tour for 17 attractions including: Pouss-Pouss, Fiesta, Kamac, Stargate, Dshunke, Big Wheel, River Slide, Hot Air Balloon, Fun House, Slide, Trampoline, 7D Cinema, Tree climbing, 5D Simulator. Countermark to exchange against the pass at the central case located at the entrance.', '\n     Description détaillée \n                		Manèges, friandises et sensations... Comme chaque année, l\'Azur Park s’installe à proximité du rond point de la Foux à Gassin !&nbsp; Plus de 35 attractions pour petits et grands vous y attendent.Le Pass Extrême comprend 1 tour pour les 5&nbsp; attractions suivantes :&nbsp;Sky Rider, Ejection Seat, Typhoon Flight Men, Playball, Atmosfear.&nbsp;\n\nLe Pass Fun comprend 1 tour pour 19 attractions dont :&nbsp;Typhoon (chaise), Bumper Boat, Dschunke, Grande Roue, Playball, River Slide, Montgolfières, Fun House, Toboggan, Accrobranche, Carrousel 1900, Cinéma 7D, Trampoline, Atmosfear, Stargate, Crazy Mouse.\n\nLe Baby Pass comprend 1 tour pour 15 attractions dont :&nbsp;Mini Pouss-Pouss, Formule 1, Tacots 1900, Train des Pignes, Bounty, Toboggan, Aladin, Petit Manège, Super Rally ou La Pomme, Cuzco, Jumping Frog, Dragoon, Caroussel 1900, Trampoline.\n\nLe Little Pass comprend 1 tour pour 17 attractions dont :&nbsp;Pouss-Pouss﻿, Fiesta, Kamac, Stargate, Dshunke, Grande Roue, River Slide, Montgolfières, Fun House, Toboggan, Trampoline, Cinéma 7D, Accrobranche, Bumper Boat, Simulateur 5D.Contremarque à échanger contre le pass à la caisse centrale située à l\'entrée.	\n    ', '', '', '', '310 Avenue de la Côte d\'Argent', 'Gassin', '83580', 'FR', '', '43.261078;6.578348', '', 'https://www.meyclub.com/public/image/produit/Gassin.jpg', '14,20€', 'Thu Nov 16 2017 10:27:56 GMT+0100 (CET)'),
