(1233, '5a0d5cb9e914587ec1459972', 'GO', 'STAGE PILOTAGE GEOPARC ST DIE DES VOSGES', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description Place: SAINT DIÉ DES VOSGES EXPERTPILOT: GEOPARC - Saint Dié des Vosges circuit (1h from Nancy and Strasbourg) With a 2500 meter long track, the route of the Géoparc de Saint-Dié circuit has been designed for to meet all the requirements of the circuit control: long straight, short turn, long parabola, chaining in support ... Safety is also a strong point of the track and the installations of track. The 2,500 m2 covered stands and the footbridge on the track allow the attendants to see the circuit 100% from the stands and enjoy the show. Unique comfort in the East! Length: 2500m Width: 12m Offer a Pack &#39;&#39; GIFT CHECK &#39;&#39; and allow the trainee to choose his formula and his car. It is used as a gift voucher valid on the basis of the amount of the Pack: the beneficiary chooses his formula among all the formulas ExpertPILOT. It can complete to go to a higher formula. Packages can be accumulated. 4 PACKS available offering a formula to choose from several proposals: - &#39;&#39; PACK 99 &#39;&#39; to 99 euros (choose category 4) - &#39;&#39; PACK 149 &#39;&#39; to 149 euros (choose category 3) - &#39;&#39; PACK 199 &#39; &#39;to 199 euros (choose category 2) -&#39; &#39;PACK 249&#39; &#39;to 249 euros (choose category 1) Included in the course: Briefing of the pilot with the instructors 2 passenger reconnaissance laps Driving behind the wheel Vehicles Graduation at the end of the internship How does it work? You offer a good voucher valid for 1 year. The beneficiary then makes his own appointment. Important: Mandatory driving license to be provided on the day of the training course.', '\n             Description détaillée \n        Lieu : SAINT DIÉ DES VOSGES\nSTAGES AUTO EXPERTPILOT :\n\nGEOPARC - Circuit de Saint Dié des Vosges (1h de Nancy et Strasbourg)\n\nAvec une piste de 2500 mètres de long, le tracé du circuit du Géoparc d