(1247, '5a0d5cbae914587ec145997c', 'SP', 'Gym SuédoiseForfait EKO TrimestrielForfait EKO Ann', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description 4 good reasons to get into Swedish Gym: 1. A FULL SPORT: Warm-up, Cardio, Strengthening muscles, Stretching ... all in an hour! THE PLEASURE OF BOUGER: In circle around the animator, one reproduces its movements following the music! 3. THE GYM FOR ALL: 9 different intensities so that you find the course adapted to your physical condition and your envy! EKO Package: Up to 350 classes per week on the entire schedule, reservation option included, unlimited access - TOPP Package: Access to the entire schedule, reservation option included, unlimited accessGym Swedish® is a complete sport developed in collaboration with doctors, physiotherapists and osteopaths. The movements are easy to make and allow to work well the heart and the muscles. At the rhythm of a lively music, the movements are chained judiciously for a maximum energy expenditure without exhaustion. This subtle combination of music and physical exercise is a source of joy, good humor and well-being. A session of Swedish Gym® is a privileged opportunity to take care of oneself, to let off steam in a convivial atmosphere, without any notion of performance. To find your room and the package that fits you Click here.', '\n     Description détaillée \n                		4 bonnes raisons de se mettre à la Gym Suédoise® : 1. UN SPORT COMPLET : Échauffement, Cardio, Renforcement musculaire, Étirements ... le tout en une petite heure !2. LE PLAISIR DE BOUGER : En cercle autour de l\'animateur, on reproduit ses mouvements en suivant la musique ! 3.\n LA GYM POUR TOUS : 9 intensités différentes pour que vous trouviez le \ncours adapté à votre condition physique et à votre envie !4. SE DÉPENSER SANS SE RUINER : Découvrez nos différents forfaits avec Meyclub en accès illimité !Nouveaux abonnements : -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Forfait EKO : Jusqu’à 350 cours 