(1258, '5a0d5cbbe914587ec1459987', 'SP', 'L\'Espace Bikram Paris Offre découverte 30 joursIll', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description The Practice: Duration of a course: 1h30Temperature in the room: 40 ° CMethode: 26 Asanas *, 2 exercises of Pranayama * &quot;Never too old, never too sick, never too late to start from scratch once again&quot; aged, never too bad in point, never too late to start all over againBikram ChoudhuryThe practice of Bikram Yoga is accessible to all, beginners as confirmed pupils of Bikram or other schools of Yoga. It does not require any special prerequisites, training or fitness. Allowing a more natural flexibility of the body, the heat makes it possible to carry out a deep work without injuring itself. Sweating due to stress contributes to cleansing the skin and eliminating toxins. After a few sessions, you will begin to sculpt your figure, find a fresh complexion and a soft skin. A practice of 3 times a week is recommended to begin to quickly feel the benefits. Despite this rhythm, you will still have the pleasure of doing you good, although the results will be longer to be felt. * Asana: pose of Hatha Yoga * Pranayama: science of respirationThe Benefits &quot;From fingertips toes to the toes, all over, inside out ... &quot;From the tips of the fingers to the tips of the toes, bones to the skin, everywhere, from the inside out ... Bikram ChoudhuryThe 26 poses practiced Bikram yoga make the body work in depth. All systems are solicited: lymphatic, nervous, muscular, bone, articular, digestive, respiratory, immune, hormonal. Bikram yoga brings you immediate well-being. With regular practice, each course deepens the effects.- Reduction of stress- Improvement of blood circulation- Durable relief of back pain- Strengthening of the immune system- Softening and control of so-called muscle tone and refinement of the silhouette- Regulation of weight - Self-revaluationOur formulas: Discovery offer 30 days: Unlimited for 30 consecutive days Va