(1260, '5a0d5cbce914587ec1459989', 'SP', 'Lady Mom Salle de sport pour les femmes (63)Abonne', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description Lady Mom is a women&#39;s gym so that they can meet each other in a warm atmosphere, a place in their image where they can evacuate everyday stress with group lessons, a cardio area and specially adapted bodybuilding to their needs and objectives, a place where the members are primarily for their well-being. Well-being goes hand in hand with pleasure, which is why the club offers a &quot;relaxation area&quot; where members can quench their thirst and talk about a cool drink, a coffee, tea or a meal made by sports dieticians. Speakers are also present in our &quot;wellness area&quot; where you can enjoy massage, manicure, pedicure, hairdressing, make-up, nails ... etc ... Moreover, a hammam is at your disposal for a maximum relaxation and a skin in full form, purified and cleaned. A shopping area also offers aesthetic products, food supplements, clothes and equipment dedicated to the sporting activity. Knowing that many women are also moms, our concept is based on the presence of a nursery for the 3 months - 10 years The goal is to eliminate this problem which often blocks moms who wish to play sports, so they can take care of them without worrying about their children in a pleasant and warm environment. Their pieces of cabbage are taken in they will be able to contribute to their development, education and socialization in living spaces specially adapted to them with all the specificities of hygiene related to their environment. group coaches are given by state-qualified coaches, each of them is specialized in different domains. Many specific courses are also set up with the partnership of health professionals: pregnant woman, post-childbirth, seniors, overweight and obesity ... we will endeavor to offer all women the means of to achieve their objectives. In a spirit of conviviality you can regularly meet around a cocktail in an 