(1287, '5a0d5cbee914587ec14599a4', 'SP', 'Hightech BB Spa - Spa des Sens (92)Carte Cadeau 30', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Detailed description Bourg-la-Reine (92) Near the RER train station in Bourg-la-Reine and not far from the Sceaux park, discover the Hightech BB Spa, the ideal address for body and facial treatments from the most advanced methods. Discover a beautiful design area where the blue soothes and recalls the benefits of the sea. In this harmonious setting, you are immediately at ease to enjoy innovative services.Through targeted protocols, support products THALGO and EVADESENS, formulated from natural products, your body finds all its curve and your face is brighter than ever. Relax with the massage that invites you to travel and escape. Take full care of yourself at Hightech BB Spa. Hydrojet 40 min mattress therapy: Leg lightweight effect guaranteed. Lying down on a heated water mattress, you begin your care by wrapping strips impregnated with slimming, draining and firming active principles. Then you continue your relaxation by a massage of the head to the feet. Slimming discovery 30min: The slimming program i-Pulse 5.1 is based on an analysis report of your morphology to determine and identify the areas to be treated. This equipment concentrates the most innovative technologies for an effective and lasting thinning: - Ultrasound, actively acting for the elimination of cellulite - Low frequency currents, for burning calories - Muscle retonification, stimulating the elimination of fat - Lymphatic drainage, eliminating toxins and promoting circulation At the end of the session, your slimming coach will offer you the cure best suited to your needs.Massage: Discover our different massages of the world (Balinese, lomi-lomi, Californian, stone-warm ...) in a relaxing atmosphere and into intoxicating scents. Gift card: Discover the choice: a well-being massage discovered, a facial treatment coup d&#39;éclat Thalgo or a session of hydrojet.', '\n     Description 