(1980, '5a0d5ccee914587ec1459a39', 'GO', '\n						Croisière dîner Réveillon du Nouvel An et I', 'Carte Jeune France', 'Description Come and celebrate the New Year&#39;s Eve Dinner Cruise, discover the magic of the Seine and enchant with the most prestigious monuments in Paris, specially illuminated for the holidays. All tables are located on the banks of the Seine to allow everyone to enjoy the capital in absolute comfort. The magic will perform for this evening of December 31 to the sound of the first notes of violin and piano. Let yourself be enchanted by the musicians accompanying this dinner cruise with timeless, international and classic French classics. A bright Paris combined with a tasty menu, specially designed for the occasion by the Chef, will leave each guest at this evening of unique memories. Good to knowValidity: December 31st Embarkation: 19h30 Departure time: 21h, except in exceptional cases Duration: 3h30 non-stop Back at the pier at 00h30 End of the service at dawn Animation performed live by an orchestra. Place of departure: At the foot of the Eiffel Tower - Port de la Bourdonnais - Paris 7th arrondissement / For check-in to show pontoons n ° 5 or n ° 7 Your ticket is an electronic ticket, you only have to present your confirmation email on the day of your cruise Access: Metro Bir Hakeim (line 6), Trocadéro (lines 6 and 9) Unique menu starting from 15 persons quai Branly) Correct clothing required (no jeans, no shorts, no sneakers) Force majeure, or &quot;water fortunes&quot;, such as floods or other climatic conditions, may force the service provider to modify the cruising route ATTENTION: for any reservation made on 31/12, the cancellation conditions are as follows: non cancellable, non-modifiable, non-refundable.', '\n                                                    Description\n                                                \n\n	Venez fêter le Réveillon de la Saint Sylvestre autour d\'une croisière dîner, découvrez toute la magie des bord